*Eusebius of Caesarea, &quot;Historia Ecclesiastica&quot;.
* Aelius Lampridius, Aelius Spartianus, Julius Capitolinus, Trebellius Pollio, Vulcatius Gallicanus, &amp; Flavius Vopiscus, &quot;Historia Augusta&quot; (Augustan History).
